<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78bab78b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s831n–2"><num value="831n–2">§ 831n–2.</num><heading> Bonds; limitation of issuance under sections 831n and 831n–1</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No bonds shall be issued by the Corporation after the date of enactment of this section under section 831n or 831n–1 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78bab78c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1933-05-18/ch32/s15b">May 18, 1933, ch. 32, § 15b</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/act/1939-07-26/ch366">July 26, 1939, ch. 366</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/53/1083">53 Stat. 1083</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id78bab78d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id78bab78e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id78bab78f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">The date of enactment of this section, referred to in text, probably means <date date="1939-07-26">July 26, 1939</date>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
